            <div type="transcript" id="F546A">
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>I prayed, at first, a little<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 Girl,</l>
                    <l>Because they told me to - </l>
                    <l>But stopped, when qualified<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 to guess </l>
                    <l>How prayer would feel - to me - </l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>If I<add type="alternate" extent="believed">supposed</add>
 believed God looked<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 around,</l>
                    <l>Each time my Childish eye </l>
                    <l>Fixed full, and steady, on<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 his own </l>
                    <l>In<add type="alternate" extent="Childish">solemn -</add>
 Childish honesty - </l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>And told him what I'd<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 like, today, </l>
                    <l>And parts of his far plan</l>
                    <l>That baffled me - </l>
                    <l>The<add type="alternate" extent="mingled">under - &amp;#x2022; further</add>
 mingled side </l>
                    <l>Of his Divinity -<app type="division"><lem><pb/></lem></app>
 </l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>And often since, in Danger, </l>
                    <l>I count the force 'twould<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 be</l>
                    <l>To have a God so strong<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 as that </l>
                    <l>To hold<add type="alternate" extent="my life">the light</add>
 my life for me </l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>Till I could<add type="alternate" extent="take the">Catch my</add>
 take the Balance </l>
                    <l>That<add type="alternate" extent="tips so frequent">slips so easy</add>
 tips so frequent, now, </l>
                    <l>It takes me all the while<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 to poise -</l>
                    <l><add type="alternate" extent="">It is&#x27;nt steady - tho&#x27; -</add>
And then - it does'nt stay - </l>
                </lg>

